Line3.FB72F: For a hundred generations, Hell itself imprisoned Father Inarius, but they could not break him. He cast off his infernal shackles and returned to us.
Line5.FB72F: And now he will guide the faithful along the path of deliverance.
VoiceDir3.FB72F: Very pious, excited. Telling a grand tale about her benefactor, the angel Inarius.
